OL,5,Cincrease
OL,7,FGas and electric bills look set to
OL,8,Fbecome even more expensive next year
OL,9,Fafter energy regulator Ofgem announced
OL,10,Fplans to up the energy price cap, as
OL,11,FITV News' Louise Scott reports
OL,13,FThe average household energy bill is
OL,14,Fset to rise again from January, as
OL,15,FOfgem announced a 1.2% increase to the
OL,16,Fenergy price cap.
OL,18,FThis is the regulator's second
OL,19,Fconsecutive rise this winter, after
OL,20,Fthe price cap increased by 10% in
OL,21,FOctober.
