OL,7,FOfgem said average household bills
OL,8,Fwill rise by #21 a year or around
OL,9,F#1.75 per month.
OL,11,FTim Jarvis, director general of
OL,12,Fmarkets at Ofgem, said: "While today's
OL,13,Fchange means the cap has remained
OL,14,Frelatively stable, we understand that
OL,15,Fthe cost of energy remains a challenge
OL,16,Ffor too many households.
