OL,7,FA Labour Party spokesperson,
OL,8,Fcommenting on the energy price cap
OL,9,Fannouncement, said: "The Conservatives
OL,10,Ftrashed Britain's energy security by
OL,11,Fleaving us exposed to global shocks
OL,12,Fand working people are still paying
OL,13,Fthe price. From banning onshore wind
OL,14,Fto failing to deliver new nuclear,
OL,15,Ftheir reckless decisions sent bills
OL,16,Fsoaring.
