OL,7,F"Labour is fixing the mess the
OL,8,FConservatives created, with our clean
OL,9,Fenergy mission that will protect
OL,10,Fconsumers and boost our energy
OL,11,Fsecurity."
OL,13,FThe energy price cap was introduced by
OL,14,Fthe government in January 2019 and
OL,15,Fsets a maximum price that energy
OL,16,Fsuppliers can charge consumers in
OL,17,FEngland, Scotland and Wales for each
OL,18,Fkilowatt hour (kWh) of energy they use.
