OL,7,FIt does not limit total bills, because
OL,8,Fhouseholders still pay for the amount
OL,9,Fof energy they consume.
OL,11,FWhile the cap is significantly lower
OL,12,Fthan at the peak of the energy crisis,
OL,13,Fwhich was fuelled by Russia's invasion
OL,14,Fof Ukraine in February 2022, prices
OL,15,Fare still "very sensitive to global
OL,16,Fevents" and supply concerns tied to
OL,17,Fgeopolitical tensions, Cornwall
OL,18,FInsight said.
