OL,7,FCraig Lowrey, principal consultant at
OL,8,FCornwall Insight, said: "Supply
OL,9,Fconcerns have kept the market as
OL,10,Fvolatile as earlier in the year and
OL,11,Fadditional charges have remained
OL,12,Frelatively stable, so prices have
OL,13,Fstayed flat.
OL,15,F"While we may have seen this coming,
OL,16,Fthe news that prices will not drop
OL,17,Ffrom the rises in the autumn will
OL,18,Fstill be disappointing to many as we
OL,19,Fmove into the colder months."
